{"tid":2128579,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦都倒掛國旗，牙泰一次半次有咩大不了？向前看啦","createTime":"2020-07-28T05:14:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:58:08.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7ad06b9aa736af3e24588386a15f65b21a15e098","tid":2128579,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190412/_2019041220023054964.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190412%2F_2019041220023054964.jpg&h=55526fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/c7aa3c/f/800x0/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161019/photo/bkn-20161019114053258-1019_00822_001_01b.jpg?20161019163034\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fc7aa3c%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161019%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20161019114053258-1019_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20161019163034&h=cd605031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>就玷污這一點而言，與其他數個元素一起來看，其實是頗具體地就着國旗的原形、原狀而定，如果令國旗受到具體侮辱，便會觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》，例如焚燒肯定是，因為是燒毀了；毀損，即扯破了，大家理解嗎？塗劃，即在上面劃了東西；踐踏，即踩在它上面，大家都理解嗎？但是，何謂&quot;玷污&quot;呢？<span class=\"red\">小弟所干犯的玷污，便是因為我的手沒有消毒，然後把國旗倒轉，這便屬玷污。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在《國旗及國徽條例》的實際操作上，有這 5 點作為基本的所謂 indicator(指標)--我說&quot;所謂&quot;，如果這些概念不正確，律師又會指正我--<span class=\"red\">但是，《條例草案》中關於侮辱國歌的罪行可以是&quot;任何方式&quot;，即官方說怎樣便怎樣，大家理解嗎？</span><br />\n法庭在判決我倒插國旗一案中，引用了吳恭劭案，令我被&quot;砌生豬肉&quot;。由於判決是在裁判法院頒下，小弟沒錢上訴至高等法院，便唯有強吞下去。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"7bf96670877d0a31f2394cfad38222eafaaf09e6","tid":2128579,"uid":17506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T05:15:05.000Z","msg":"牙泰倒掛左唔只一枝旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4f2391a595e682df216013753f6f7814ab0ce4","tid":212